{"id":60,"ayahs":[{"number":78,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ مِنْهُمْ لَفَرِيقًۭا يَلْوُۥنَ أَلْسِنَتَهُم بِٱلْكِتَٰبِ لِتَحْسَبُوهُ مِنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَمَا هُوَ مِنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَيَقُولُونَ هُوَ مِنْ عِندِ ٱللَّهِ وَمَا هُوَ مِنْ عِندِ ٱللَّهِ وَيَقُولُونَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ ٱلْكَذِبَ وَهُمْ يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"And, behold, there are indeed some among them who distort the Bible with their tongues, so as to make you think that [what they say] is from the Bible, the while it is not from the Bible; and who say, \"This is from God,\" the while it is not from God: and thus do they tell a lie about God, being well aware [that it is a lie].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/371.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":63518,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63519,"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ","translation":"তাদের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63520,"position":3,"arabic":"لَفَرِيقًۭا","translation":"অবশ্যই একদল (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63521,"position":4,"arabic":"يَلْوُۥنَ","translation":"তারা মুড়াতে থাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63522,"position":5,"arabic":"أَلْسِنَتَهُم","translation":"তাদের জিহবাগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63523,"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাব (পাঠে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63524,"position":7,"arabic":"لِتَحْسَبُوهُ","translation":"তাকে তোমরা যেন মনে কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63525,"position":8,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অংশ (হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63526,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাবের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_078_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63527,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"অথচ না","audi